column1: #Text=The deaths exceed by nearly 10 per cent, the average number of the corresponding quarters of four previous years.
#Text=An increase in the births may be partly accounted for by there having been a hospital lately established for soldiers* wives in my subdistrict.

#Text=—We understand that the Dean and Chapter of Salisbury Cathedral have granted permission to this admirable society for the holding of a grand choral festival of the united cbnrch choirs in the diocese, in the Cathedral, next year.
#Text=The number of voices, it is expected, will exceed 1000.
#Text=Spinney has been appointed organist and choir-master at this Church.
#Text=There is an understanding, however, that the duties of the former office are to be discharged by Miss Mattie Spinney.
#Text=Mr. no intention of resigning the poet of organist, which be has so long held, at Sutton Waldron.
